1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:50,540
All right.

4
00:00:52,020 --> 00:00:57,380
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

5
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:00,539
We're already husband and wife.

6
00:01:00,540 --> 00:01:02,300
Why go through all this?

7
00:01:05,380 --> 00:01:08,400
It may seem a little old fashioned,

8
00:01:09,620 --> 00:01:10,740
but...

9
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:15,020
Back then, it was Gu Shaoyan
marrying Xue Wan.

10
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:17,140
But now,

11
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:19,460
it's me, Lu Shaoyuan,

12
00:01:20,580 --> 00:01:22,060
who wants to marry Zhuang Yunqiu.

13
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:24,660
So...

14
00:01:24,900 --> 00:01:26,580
Miss Zhuang Yunqiu,

15
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:31,100
would you be willing
to marry Mr. Lu Shaoyuan?

16
00:01:31,540 --> 00:01:36,210
♪A happy game that began within a dream♪

17
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:37,850
I do.

18
00:01:38,850 --> 00:01:44,849
♪Can you still see it within the night?♪

19
00:01:44,850 --> 00:01:51,320
♪The life I long for
is tangled within it♪

20
00:01:51,450 --> 00:01:55,019
♪Forcing me to trade pain for the past♪

21
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:55,990
Beautiful.

22
00:01:57,170 --> 00:01:59,980
♪In this world♪

23
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:21,740
♪Love is a beautiful exchange♪

24
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:27,600
♪In that moment, our hearts became one♪

25
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:33,900
♪Breaking through
what reality could never allow♪

26
00:02:34,580 --> 00:02:38,579
♪Casting aside everything meaningless♪

27
00:02:38,579 --> 00:02:41,099
Something terrible has happened.
The soldiers guarding the prisoners are dead.

28
00:02:41,099 --> 00:02:42,620
The prisoners were taken too.

29
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,540
- What?
- What?

30
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,540
- Have they been found?
- Not yet.

31
00:02:56,740 --> 00:02:57,380
Keep searching.

32
00:03:01,740 --> 00:03:02,539
How is it?

33
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:03,550
Any news?

34
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,980
We've searched the entire city.
There's still no sign of them.

35
00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:10,020
There's something else
that's been bothering me.

36
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:13,180
Cheng Yi hasn't returned in a long time.
Could something have happened to him?

37
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:14,980
Cheng Yi...

38
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:16,860
Last night, I sent him
to prepare the church.

39
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,900
By now, he should've returned already.

40
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:22,020
But it's also possible
that he discovered Gu Shaoyan escaping

41
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:23,460
and went after him before we did.

42
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,060
Let's wait a little longer.

43
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,140
All right.

44
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:39,300
Commander. There are large numbers
of soldiers searching outside.

45
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:41,820
My dear brother

46
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,860
would never imagine

47
00:03:44,980 --> 00:03:48,020
that I'm hiding
in my real wife's family home.

48
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:51,620
Everything was arranged by fate.

49
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:54,580
Heaven truly hasn't abandoned me.

50
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:58,300
And now we still have him.

51
00:03:58,540 --> 00:04:00,540
Commander. What should we do with him?

52
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,180
Keep a close eye on him for now.

53
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:04,340
Yes, Commander.

54
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:09,420
Move.

55
00:04:55,660 --> 00:04:56,500
Commander.

56
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:58,459
I made this medicinal soup for you.

57
00:04:58,460 --> 00:05:00,180
It'll help your recovery.

58
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:02,060
Thank you, Miss Xue.

59
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:04,900
And thank you for taking me in.

60
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:07,820
May I ask...

61
00:05:08,380 --> 00:05:10,859
Who was the man in the sack just now?

62
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:13,020
And what exactly is going on here?

63
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:15,700
This whole thing

64
00:05:16,020 --> 00:05:17,620
was all because
I failed to see the truth.

65
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:22,260
I mistook Zhuang Yunqiu for you

66
00:05:22,860 --> 00:05:24,780
and believed all her sweet lies.

67
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:26,380
I truly never expected

68
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:29,060
her to be so manipulative,

69
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:32,179
so skilled at winning people over.

70
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:32,979
By the time

71
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:34,100
I realized it,

72
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:36,820
she had already slowly taken

73
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:39,220
all my power into her own hands.

74
00:05:39,540 --> 00:05:41,740
Zhuang Yunqiu
is really that calculating?

75
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:44,260
But you trusted her so much before.

76
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:45,899
When I went to tell you
who I really was,

77
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:47,179
you believed her completely.

78
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:49,020
She forced me to do all of it.

79
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:51,980
She said I wasn't convincing enough,

80
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:53,980
that I wasn't close enough to her

81
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,620
or distant enough from you.

82
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:57,300
That's why

83
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,540
she locked me up.

84
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:02,260
What did you say?

85
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:04,020
Now that I think about it,

86
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:06,300
it's truly hard to speak of.

87
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:08,300
I'm the Commander of an entire city,

88
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:11,580
yet I was manipulated by a woman.

89
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:14,539
But you're the Commander of Yancheng.

90
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:16,220
How could Zhuang Yunqiu,
a woman on her own,

91
00:06:16,260 --> 00:06:17,579
possibly do anything to you?

92
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:19,300
That's because
you don't know her methods.

93
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,180
You saw the man

94
00:06:26,380 --> 00:06:27,740
tied up today too.

95
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:29,620
He used to be my adjutant,

96
00:06:30,220 --> 00:06:31,740
yet he betrayed me

97
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:34,380
and became her lackey.

98
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:37,580
How could Zhuang Yunqiu
become like this?

99
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:40,740
Miss Xue has been overseas all this time,
so there are things you don't know.

100
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:42,900
Back then,
under Commander-in-Chief's orders,

101
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:46,140
I executed the Zhuang family
for trafficking opium.

102
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,300
Zhuang Yunqiu
has held a grudge ever since.

103
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,540
She carefully planned her marriage to me

104
00:06:51,340 --> 00:06:52,740
for the sake of revenge.

105
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:56,780
But I've heard about that matter too.

106
00:06:57,260 --> 00:06:59,219
She told me you framed her family.

107
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:01,430
What she's best at
is twisting right and wrong.

108
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:02,980
When she stayed at your house,

109
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:04,740
she often insulted the Xue family too,

110
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,260
saying Xue Tian treated her poorly

111
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:09,260
and that the Xue family
ignored her completely.

112
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:10,980
How unreasonable.

113
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,219
I even let her stay in my home

114
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:14,619
out of respect for old ties,

115
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:16,300
yet she spoke of my brother like that.

116
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:18,199
Before she got married,

117
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,219
I even embroidered

118
00:07:19,220 --> 00:07:20,650
a Red Spider Lily on her.

119
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,280
I never expected her
to deceive me like this.

120
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,940
We're both victims.

121
00:07:26,500 --> 00:07:28,740
I understand that feeling.

122
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,300
I doubted her before too,

123
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:33,620
but she was too cunning.

124
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:36,499
I also doubted the things she said.

125
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:38,419
One moment she'd say
you were a good person,

126
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:40,719
and the next
she'd call you hypocritical.

127
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:43,650
I truly couldn't tell which of her words
were true and which were false.

128
00:07:44,420 --> 00:07:46,820
This is all my fault.

129
00:07:47,260 --> 00:07:48,139
And now,

130
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:50,060
she's even found a puppet to replace me.

131
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:52,260
The fact that I'm still alive

132
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:54,420
is already a blessing.

133
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:57,740
This isn't your fault.

134
00:07:58,100 --> 00:07:59,140
If anyone's to blame,

135
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:01,419
it's me for believing her

136
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:03,220
and letting her marry you in my place.

137
00:08:03,740 --> 00:08:04,859
But don't worry.

138
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,620
Stay at my house and recover in peace.

139
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:09,140
I'll help you take back
your position as Commander.

140
00:08:14,180 --> 00:08:16,700
Then thank you, Miss Xue.

141
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:46,230
Gu Shaoyan.

142
00:08:46,860 --> 00:08:48,380
My name is Gu Nianchi.

143
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,100
My sworn younger brother.

144
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:54,650
Who is your younger brother?

145
00:08:56,220 --> 00:08:57,619
The lives in that poor village

146
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:58,910
can't be saved anymore,

147
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:02,300
but you can still save your own life.

148
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:03,580
Tell me.

149
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:07,580
Where did Lu Shaoyuan
hide the military seal?

150
00:09:07,940 --> 00:09:09,110
And I'll let you go.

151
00:09:10,290 --> 00:09:11,510
Keep dreaming.

152
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:13,500
I'm not telling you.

153
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,860
I'll never betray Shaoyuan.

154
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,500
So you really do know.

155
00:09:20,580 --> 00:09:22,540
If you don't want to suffer,

156
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:24,700
then you'd better talk.

157
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:28,040
I do know.

158
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:30,940
But I'll never tell you.

159
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:39,920
What a nuisance.

160
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:51,810
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

161
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:58,440
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

162
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:02,520
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

163
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:05,870
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

164
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:11,160
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

165
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:17,470
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

166
00:10:18,530 --> 00:10:24,130
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

167
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:28,050
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

168
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:31,249
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

169
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:36,389
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

170
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:40,709
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

171
00:10:40,710 --> 00:10:43,289
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

172
00:10:43,290 --> 00:10:45,569
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

173
00:10:45,570 --> 00:10:49,119
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

174
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:53,649
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

175
00:10:53,650 --> 00:10:56,180
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

176
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,269
♪Still I walk into♪

177
00:10:58,270 --> 00:11:01,869
♪The trap you set without regret♪

178
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:05,919
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

179
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:08,499
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

180
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,659
♪A stand in can never cross♪

181
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:14,099
♪The shortest distance between us♪

182
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:19,070
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

183
00:11:19,230 --> 00:11:23,900
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

184
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:28,249
♪A substitute♪

185
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:33,250
♪Needs no reason♪

